original_title: 51st death anniversary of late Philip Gunawardene
original_body_lines: The incumbent President Ranil Wickremesinghe, together with Prime Minister Dinesh Gunawardene, former Presidents Mahinda Rajapaksa and Maithripala Sirisena together with Speaker Mahinda Yapa Abeywardene, are seen at a commemoration ceremony  held at the BMICH to mark the 51st death anniversary of late socialist party leader Philip Gunawardene.  Pix by Nimalsiri Edirisinghe
